{"tid":1488891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對家nazi salute俾我嘅啓示——避免關公災難","createTime":"2019-08-19T17:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T00:08:42.000Z","uid":267879,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"73f7ef27eb12ec8674dd3afec18111b87a03a066","tid":1488891,"uid":267879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:25:39.000Z","msg":"對家愛國rally出現九唔搭八納粹手勢，香港人除左幸災樂禍之外，更要反思一下自己嘅言行，<span style=\"color: red;\">特別係當你喺twitter上/對住外媒時嘅形象</span>。<br />\n<br />\n外國左派（或者你地認為某啲係左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）對政治正確頗為敏感。而作為香港人不得不承認嘅係，我地叫自己做國際城市，但喺種族歧視、性別歧視等議題上係極之不敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（btw你地品評完個女警對波未，你叫之前被藍絲改圖性騷擾嘅女義士情何以堪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n我係絕對唔會割蓆，亦無意喺風頭火勢下掉轉槍頭。只係想大家公關做得好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你就當成個運動係一個國際品牌</span></span></span>，好無？如果想國際社會不分左中右支持，就要盡量揾個最大公因數出嚟：右派基本上唔理你政唔政治正確，但<span style=\"color: red;\">中間同左派就要小心對待</span>。嗰啲咩蝗蟲論就收一收埋，有人提起你就用返「曱甴論」同「解放軍都比喻示威者係蝗蟲」嚟搶返個victim嚟做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於pepe呢個問題，隔離post提到，雖然有外媒係理解，但普通外國人都唔係幾明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。所以<span style=\"color: red;\">對外國人嘅文宣就盡量避免用</span>啦（文宣手足自己諗，我提議下姐）。當然而家有啲難定義咩係對外宣傳，因為佢地follow得好貼，所以我地可以考慮用下連狗、腦魔etc.<br />\n<br />\n性別方面，暫時未有外媒好關注呢個問題，但都係嗰句啦，忍忍口，想j咪私底下j囉，冇人理你平時做乜，但洗哂板咁真係好咩？同樣，我知某啲人對性小眾有啲意見，但好多同路人係性小眾，咪開口埋口攻擊人tb好無？focus返佢地係警犬呢個身分okay？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntl;dr<br />\n以前就話The revolution will not be televised<br />\n而家就唔止會被televised，仲要被televised到全世界<br />\n唔理你認唔認同嗰啲理念，但現實係政治正確係世界潮流<br />\n唔想好似強國人咁不停關公災難，就注意一下對外嘅言行<br />\n<br />\n其他大家可補充下"},{"pid":"38dd60fd3cb1310e70b3fa1661ce312f85fc5e88","tid":1488891,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1faca8eb1017758bbfaf7d161953ade32d87f1da","tid":1488891,"uid":267879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:30:51.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e7d55dabebe740203a45edd8d029fbbdbd7d3f","tid":1488891,"uid":76391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:31:00.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c15b73482cd261ce77fce53f4ac48794efbb5035","tid":1488891,"uid":267879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17535e9ff96e2b5c59aabc52a0e9834518bfe459","tid":1488891,"uid":310280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:34:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">推，順手向外輸出腦魔meme</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212ebb0a66e59aa0abda6c76bab10a3a37bb5aa6","tid":1488891,"uid":267879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:34:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"737d2a8227d7c1cd1fd98a0bf108355af86a2c60","tid":1488891,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:35:02.000Z","msg":"無錯，對外要有形象，特別係對大陸網軍，要畀全世界人知係佢地蝦緊人。"},{"pid":"6b190326f90a8ff67a0ed5b7e63560fe571a5de0","tid":1488891,"uid":86442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:35:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da50ea0ebb189604ff1657510f58ff84e82106b2","tid":1488891,"uid":86442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:36:08.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"ddb17a40480b3adb88de3a88b48ee576120e1d61","tid":1488891,"uid":29